{
  "texts": [
    "Meanwhile, the video pacing becomes smoother as our method advances the first hand-clapping node compared to the ground truth construction.In conclusion, the comparable performance of experimental results reflects the advantages of our approach, which can be inferred as follows.• Frames are represented by feature engineering, and the representation learned by the recommendation algorithm effectively reflects the representativeness of the frames.",
    "• Our manually constructed features are content rich.",
    "For keyframe recommendation, capturing the video content comprehensively is crucial.",
    "• Due to the imbalance of positive and negative samples in keyframes, expanding the number of videos will increase the number of positive samples so that the negative samples can be appropriately reduced.",
    "This processing method can improve the performance of keyframe recommendation."
  ]
}